		       <TELL
"In the ceiling above you see the outline of a panel.">)>
		<TELL
" You notice an unusual newel next to the stairs leading down.">)>>

<ROOM UPSTAIRS-HALL-EAST
      (IN ROOMS)
      (DESC "Upstairs Hall, East")
