<ROUTINE UPSTAIRS-HALL-EAST-EXIT-F ()
	 <COND (<AND <FSET? ,SACK ,HAND-ON-SACK-BIT>
		     ,SACK-IN-WINDOW>
		<TELL "You'll have to let go of the sack first." CR>
		<RFALSE>)
	       (T
		<COND (<EQUAL? ,PRSO ,P?NORTH>
		       ,BEDROOM-2)
		      (<EQUAL? ,PRSO ,P?SOUTH>
