			 <EQUAL? ,CLOSET-FLOOR ,UPSTAIRS-HALL-MIDDLE>>
		    <AND <EQUAL? ,HERE ,UPSTAIRS-HALL-MIDDLE>
			 <EQUAL? ,CLOSET-FLOOR ,ATTIC>>>
